<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>Caccelia Santika | Fashion Designer</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:wght@500;700&family=Open+Sans&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
      scroll-behavior: smooth;
    }

    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif;
      background-color: #fff;
      color: #2b2b2b;
    }

    header {
      background-image: url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1520975916090-310595a1ab79?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1500&q=80');
      background-size: cover;
      background-position: center;
      color: white;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 6rem 2rem;
    }

    header h1 {
      font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
      font-size: 3rem;
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }

    header p {
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      opacity: 0.9;
    }

    nav {
      background-color: #f8f8f8;
      padding: 1rem;
      text-align: center;
      position: sticky;
      top: 0;
      z-index: 1000;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
    }

    nav a {
      margin: 0 1.5rem;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #333;
      transition: color 0.3s;
    }

    nav a:hover {
      color: #ba5f50;
    }

    section {
      padding: 4rem 2rem;
      max-width: 1000px;
      margin: auto;
    }

    section h2 {
      font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
      font-size: 2rem;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      border-left: 5px solid #ba5f50;
      padding-left: 1rem;
    }

    .portfolio {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
      gap: 1.5rem;
    }

    .portfolio img {
      width: 100%;
      border-radius: 12px;
      box-shadow: 0 6px 12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      transition: transform 0.4s ease, box-shadow 0.4s ease;
    }

    .portfolio img:hover {
      transform: scale(1.03);
      box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
    }

    .contact p {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      line-height: 1.8;
    }

    a {
      color: #ba5f50;
    }

    footer {
      background-color: #2b2b2b;
      color: #fff;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 2rem;
    }

    @media (max-width: 600px) {
      nav a {
        margin: 0 0.5rem;
        display: inline-block;
      }

      header h1 {
        font-size: 2rem;
      }

      section {
        padding: 2rem 1rem;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

<header>
  <h1>Caccelia Santika</h1>
  <p>Fashion Designer | Visionary | Creator of Elegant Silhouettes</p>
</header>

<nav>
  <a href="#about">Tentang</a>
  <a href="#portfolio">Portofolio</a>
  <a href="#contact">Kontak</a>
</nav>

<section id="about">
  <h2>Tentang Saya</h2>
  <p>
    Saya adalah seorang fashion designer dengan dedikasi tinggi terhadap keindahan, inovasi, dan ekspresi melalui desain. Selama lebih dari 7 tahun, saya telah menciptakan berbagai koleksi dari ready-to-wear hingga couture, menghadirkan perpaduan antara estetika modern dan identitas budaya. Setiap karya saya adalah pernyataan, setiap garis adalah cerita.
  </p>
</section>

<section id="portfolio">
  <h2>Portofolio</h2>
  <div class="portfolio">
    <img src="https://source.unsplash.com/400x500/?fashion,model" alt="Koleksi 1">
    <img src="https://source.unsplash.com/400x500/?fashion,design" alt="Koleksi 2">
    <img src="https://source.unsplash.com/400x500/?couture" alt="Koleksi 3">
    <img src="https://source.unsplash.com/400x500/?style,fashion" alt="Koleksi 4">
  </div>
</section>

<section id="contact" class="contact">
  <h2>Kontak</h2>
  <p>Email: <a href="mailto:caccelia.fashion@gmail.com">caccelia.fashion@gmail.com</a></p>
  <p>Instagram: <a href="https://instagram.com/caccelia.design" target="_blank">@caccelia.design</a></p>
  <p>LinkedIn: <a href="https://linkedin.com/in/cacceliasantika" target="_blank">Caccelia Santika</a></p>
</section>

<footer>
  <p>&copy; 2025 Caccelia Santika. All rights reserved.</p>
</footer>

</body>
</html>
